"```json{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Union imposed new sanctions on Russia, targeting entities supporting Russia's war efforts. The EU also sanctioned businesses in India and China with ties to Russia's war. Meanwhile, Somalia agreed to let Turkey defend its territorial waters to address threats from abroad.\",            \"english_title\": \"European Union Sanctions on Russia and Somalia-Turkey Agreement\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Uni\u00f3n Europea impuso sanciones nuevas a Rusia, apuntando a entidades que apoyan los esfuerzos de guerra de Rusia. La UE tambi\u00e9n sancion\u00f3 negocios en India y China con v\u00ednculos a la guerra de Rusia. Mientras tanto, Somalia acord\u00f3 dejar que Turqu\u00eda defienda sus aguas territoriales para enfrentar amenazas del extranjero.\",            \"translated_title\": \"European Union Sanctions on Russia and Somalia-Turkey Agreement\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Boeing replaced the boss of the factory building 737 Max 9 jets after an incident where a door shed during flight. South Africa's finance minister outlined plans to raise additional funds through fiscal measures and increased levies on goods due to economic challenges.\",            \"english_title\": \"Boeing Leadership Shake-up and South Africa's Budget Plans\",            \"translated_version\": \"Boeing reemplaz\u00f3 al jefe de la f\u00e1brica que construye los aviones 737 Max 9 despu\u00e9s de un incidente donde una puerta se desprendi\u00f3 durante el vuelo. El ministro de finanzas de Sud\u00e1frica describi\u00f3 planes para recaudar fondos adicionales a trav\u00e9s de medidas fiscales y aumentar impuestos sobre bienes debido a desaf\u00edos econ\u00f3micos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Boeing Leadership Shake-up and South Africa's Budget Plans\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Rio Tinto approved a $20bn mining project in Guinea, West Africa, expected to start delivering iron ore next year. This project offers hope for the global mining industry after facing investor challenges in recent years.\",            \"english_title\": \"Rio Tinto's Mining Project in Guinea\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rio Tinto aprob\u00f3 un proyecto minero de $20 mil millones en Guinea, \u00c1frica Occidental, que se espera comience a entregar mineral de hierro el pr\u00f3ximo a\u00f1o. Este proyecto ofrece esperanza para la industria minera global despu\u00e9s de enfrentar desaf\u00edos de inversores en a\u00f1os recientes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rio Tinto's Mining Project in Guinea\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A Ukrainian air strike reportedly killed over 65 Russian soldiers in occupied territory in eastern Ukraine. The strike, using American-supplied rockets, followed the Russian capture of a nearby town, Avdiivka.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukrainian Air Strike in Eastern Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque a\u00e9reo ucraniano supuestamente mat\u00f3 a m\u00e1s de 65 soldados rusos en territorio ocupado en el este de Ucrania. El ataque, utilizando cohetes suministrados por Estados Unidos, sigui\u00f3 a la captura rusa de una ciudad cercana, Avdiivka.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ukrainian Air Strike in Eastern Ukraine\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Space Agency predicted that the ERS-2 satellite launched in 1995 will re-enter the atmosphere and fall to Earth. ERS-2, along with ERS-1, gathered data on various environmental factors in the 1990s.\",            \"english_title\": \"European Space Agency's Prediction on ERS-2 Satellite\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Agencia Espacial Europea predijo que el sat\u00e9lite ERS-2 lanzado en 1995 reingresar\u00e1 a la atm\u00f3sfera y caer\u00e1 a la Tierra. ERS-2, junto con ERS-1, recopil\u00f3 datos sobre varios factores ambientales en la d\u00e9cada de 1990.\",            \"translated_title\": \"European Space Agency's Prediction on ERS-2 Satellite\"        }    ]}```"